WEBVTT

1
03:17:34.200 --> 03:17:37.240 
愿上帝赐予你宽恕与平静  弗兰克
May God grant you pardon and peace, Frank.

2
03:17:37.250 --> 03:17:38.450 
我赦免你的罪
And I absolve you from your sins.

3
03:17:38.450 --> 03:17:40.950 
以圣父  圣子
In the name of the Father, and of the Son,

4
03:17:40.950 --> 03:17:43.370 
圣灵的名义  阿门
and of the Holy Spirit, amen.

5
03:17:44.120 --> 03:17:46.790 
感谢上帝  因为上帝仁慈
Give thanks to the Lord, for he is good.

6
03:17:46.950 --> 03:17:48.040 
他的慈爱
His mercy...

7
03:17:48.040 --> 03:17:50.660 
-他的慈爱永远长存  -永远长存
- His mercy endures forever. - endures forever.

8
03:17:50.660 --> 03:17:53.660 
好了  弗兰克  我很快就会再来看你
All right, Frank. I'll be back to visit, okay? Very soon.

9
03:17:53.660 --> 03:17:56.460 
大概圣诞假期后
Probably after the Christmas holidays.

10
03:17:57.080 --> 03:17:57.990 
好的
Okay.

11
03:17:58.000 --> 03:18:00.750 
-弗兰克  上帝保佑你  -你也是  谢谢
- Frank, God bless you. - You too. Thank you.

12
03:18:03.040 --> 03:18:04.120 
圣诞节到了
It's Christmas?

